WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.849
<i>Previously on "Mr. Mercedes"... </i>

00:01.850 --> 00:04.019
Ms. Linklatter, you've been found guilty

00:04.019 --> 00:06.463
of committing murder
in the second degree.

00:06.464 --> 00:09.759
I'm going to suspend the
remainder of your sentence.

00:09.760 --> 00:11.719
[APPLAUSE]

00:11.720 --> 00:13.999
- Are we on a date?
- I'm hoping that

00:14.000 --> 00:15.683
it will feel a little like a date

00:15.684 --> 00:17.892
so if we ever were to have one,

00:17.893 --> 00:20.409
<i>it won't be such a jolt.</i>

00:20.410 --> 00:23.059
<i>[BROODING MUSIC]</i>

00:23.060 --> 00:26.479
- How was it?
- It was really, really good.

00:26.480 --> 00:28.404
I was hoping to speak
to your son, Peter.

00:28.405 --> 00:29.979
He is at school.

00:29.980 --> 00:31.282
<i>I've just come from there. He's not.</i>

00:31.283 --> 00:33.449
$75,000.

00:33.450 --> 00:36.244
- For one page of Rothstein?
- I told you.

00:36.245 --> 00:38.939
You already got all the
stolen merchandise.

00:38.940 --> 00:40.479
[GROANS]

00:40.480 --> 00:41.820
I am gonna kill that fucker.

00:41.834 --> 00:43.042
No, you ain't, neither,

00:43.043 --> 00:45.379
<i>at least not until we get
ahold of those manuscripts.</i>

00:45.380 --> 00:47.119
Get the fuck out of my store!

00:47.120 --> 00:49.039
Give me those manuscripts.

00:49.040 --> 00:53.094
Now you say, "Or what?" Then I say...

00:53.095 --> 00:55.549
[GASPS, SHRIEKS]

00:55.550 --> 00:57.263
- The kid's got them.
- Saubers.

00:57.264 --> 00:59.079
- Yes.
- And you don't know

00:59.080 --> 01:00.149
where he's got them?

01:00.150 --> 01:02.169
- No.
- I don't believe you, Andy.

01:02.170 --> 01:03.339
[SHRIEKS]

01:03.340 --> 01:05.799
- You killed him?
- I had to.

01:05.800 --> 01:07.899
Jesus fucking Christ.

01:07.900 --> 01:10.460
I do get the sense that
he's mixed up in something

01:10.470 --> 01:12.039
- that's bigger than himself.
- Peter...

01:12.040 --> 01:14.739
- Pete!
<i>- Hey, where are you?</i>

01:14.740 --> 01:16.940
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:16.950 --> 01:20.369
<i>[BOB DYLAN'S "SERIES OF DREAMS"]</i>

01:20.370 --> 01:24.079
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:24.080 --> 01:26.599
<i>♪ I was thinking ♪</i>

01:26.600 --> 01:28.979
<i>♪ Of a series of dreams ♪</i>

01:28.980 --> 01:31.079
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:31.080 --> 01:32.550
<i>♪ Where nothing ♪</i>

01:32.551 --> 01:36.379
<i>♪ Comes up to the top ♪</i>

01:36.380 --> 01:38.519
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:38.520 --> 01:41.179
<i>♪ Everything ♪</i>

01:41.180 --> 01:43.489
<i>♪ Stays down where it's wounded ♪</i>

01:43.490 --> 01:45.104
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:45.105 --> 01:48.274
<i>♪ And comes ♪</i>

01:48.275 --> 01:50.860
<i>♪ To a permanent stop ♪</i>

01:50.861 --> 01:53.069
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:53.070 --> 01:55.799
<i>♪ Wasn't thinking ♪</i>

01:55.800 --> 01:57.949
<i>♪ Of anything specific ♪</i>

01:57.950 --> 02:00.519
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:00.520 --> 02:03.109
<i>♪ Just thinking ♪</i>

02:03.110 --> 02:05.119
<i>♪ Of a series of dreams ♪</i>

02:05.120 --> 02:07.739
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:07.740 --> 02:10.318
<i>♪ Just thinking ♪</i>

02:10.320 --> 02:12.339
<i>♪ Of a series of dreams ♪</i>

