Oh.

33:00.320 --> 33:03.390
- Everything okay?
- Yeah, it's fine.

33:03.398 --> 33:05.608
[KEYS TAPPING]

33:05.609 --> 33:07.611
[INDISTINCT WHISPERING]

33:09.780 --> 33:11.030
Holly, what's wrong?

33:12.740 --> 33:14.780
Okay...

33:16.460 --> 33:18.119
