and relationships, and...

33:35.515 --> 33:36.779
[SIGHS]

33:36.780 --> 33:39.479
You and me, I don't think we'd...

33:39.480 --> 33:41.009
sustain.

33:41.010 --> 33:42.799
You don't think we'd "sustain"?

33:42.800 --> 33:45.439
[STAMMERS] Wait, we
haven't even started.

33:45.440 --> 33:47.942
Exactly. Already, we're
not working out. [SCOFFS]

33:47.943 --> 33:50.729
- Did something happen?
- No, nothing happened.

33:50.730 --> 33:53.079
I just don't... don't want this,
and I really would like it

33:53.080 --> 33:55.492
if you just respected my choices.

33:57.710 --> 34:02.139
[KEYS TAPPING]

34:02.140 --> 34:03.417
Fine.

34:05.980 --> 34:07.750
Fine.

34:10.940 --> 34:14.770
[SIGHS]

34:37.110 --> 34:38.739
What the hell was that all about,

34:38.739 --> 34:40.359
