34:44.420 --> 34:46.001
personal questions about their...

34:46.002 --> 34:48.498
Oh, so I'm your boss again now, am I?

34:48.500 --> 34:51.422
A bit ago, eh, you were
a full fucking partner.

34:53.639 --> 34:55.760
I should go check on Lou.

35:06.140 --> 35:08.310
You told me she likes the guy.

35:09.880 --> 35:12.027
She does.

35:14.690 --> 35:16.419
