database. You'll be fine.

35:24.520 --> 35:27.668
No, you'll be fine! My blood
is in there. I got cut.

35:27.669 --> 35:28.979
The fuck happened?

35:28.980 --> 35:31.119
Things never go the way
they're fucking planned,

35:31.120 --> 35:32.297
