35:32.298 --> 35:33.839
She fought like a fucking wolverine!

35:33.840 --> 35:35.319
- Did you get her phone?
- Yeah, I got it.

35:35.320 --> 35:36.829
- Give it to me.
- Here.

35:36.830 --> 35:38.219
Now tape her mouth, fast.

35:38.220 --> 35:40.806
I got it, I got it, I got it,
I got it, I got it.

35:40.807 --> 35:43.391
[OWL HOOTING]

35:43.392 --> 35:45.101
Tell me when you got the mouth done.

35:45.102 --> 35:47.459
- Done.
- All right, move out of my way.

35:47.460 --> 35:49.389
[CAMERA SHUTTER SNAPPING]

35:49.390 --> 35:51.339
- What are you doing?
- I've gotta get the pictures to the gimp

35:51.340 --> 35:53.859
before he gets home.
Otherwise he'll call the police.

35:53.860 --> 35:56.649
- [GRUNTING]
- Her legs, let's go.

35:56.650 --> 35:59.079
It doesn't have to be
perfect, Morris, just do it!

35:59.080 --> 36:00.229
It's not perfect, believe me.

36:00.230 --> 36:01.899
Look at this shit job I'm doing.

36:01.900 --> 36:03.879
Shove her legs in,
close the fucking door,

36:03.880 --> 36:05.519
and let's go.

36:05.520 --> 36:08.390
Nice job...

36:11.040 --> 36:13.079
- [GRUNTS SOFTLY] See ya, fellas.
- Hey, Tom.

36:13.080 --> 36:15.960
[PHONE CHIMING]

36:20.262 --> 36:23.097
- _
- <i>[DARK MUSIC]</i>

36:23.098 --> 36:26.549
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:26.550 --> 36:28.519
[BREATHING SHAKILY]

36:28.520 --> 36:32.315
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:37.930 --> 36:39.740
She's waking up. It's about time.

36:40.830 --> 36:42.859
Hey, Marjorie.

36:42.860 --> 36:44.839
- How you doing, honey?
- [MUFFLED GRUNTING]

36:44.840 --> 36:46.399
- Oh.
- [SHRIEKS]

36:46.400 --> 36:49.999
- [GROANS]
- You feeling okay, sweetheart?

36:50.000 --> 36:52.293
[STAMMERS] I don't understand.

36:52.294 --> 36:54.789
Yeah, maybe I can help with that.

36:54.790 --> 36:59.219
See, you think you're
having a shitty day,

36:59.220 --> 37:01.839
but you know what real shit is?

37:01.840 --> 37:05.819
It's having all your days
blur into one another,

37:05.820 --> 37:09.579
not being able to distinguish
one from the next.

37:09.580 --> 37:12.659
That's my idea of hell.

37:12.660 --> 37:15.679
You will remember this day,

37:15.680 --> 37:17.530
should you live through it.

37:19.160 --> 37:20.519
I thought you were my friend.

37:20.520 --> 37:22.039
I know, sorry.

37:22.040 --> 37:24.242
You need to pick your friends better.

37:25.600 --> 37:27.119
[GRUNTING]

37:27.120 --> 37:29.099
You can pick your friends,
you can pick your nose,

37:29.100 --> 37:30.916
but you can't pick your friend's nose.

37:30.917 --> 37:33.699
Well, sometimes you can.

37:33.700 --> 37:36.879
Sometimes you can even
pick your friend's nose

37:36.880 --> 37:40.249
with another friend's... [CLICKS TONGUE]

37:40.250 --> 37:42.619
finger.

37:42.620 --> 37:46.219
Hmm? [BABBLING]

37:46.220 --> 37:48.299
- No, no, no, no!
- Here it goes.

37:48.300 --> 37:51.179
Picky, picky, picky!

37:51.180 --> 37:54.019
Oh, shit, you made a mess.

37:54.020 --> 37:55.679
- Tape her mouth back up.
- [COUGHING]

37:55.680 --> 37:58.199
Puke again, you'll be drowning.

37:58.200 --> 37:59.439
[COUGHING]

37:59.440 --> 38:02.419
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.
- [WHIMPERING]

38:02.420 --> 38:04.319
No crying now.

38:04.320 --> 38:06.079
This is exciting.

38:06.080 --> 38:08.819
Do you know who I like to
go to in challenging times?

38:08.820 --> 38:11.199
Liza Minnelli.

38:11.200 --> 38:13.099
The things she endured.

38:13.100 --> 38:16.749
Nobody ever gives that dame
enough credit, but I do.

38:16.750 --> 38:19.673
Do you know what she'd
say to you right now?

38:19.674 --> 38:23.540
She'd say, "Money."

38:26.620 --> 38:34.560
[PHONE CHIRPING]

38:44.360 --> 38:48.033
- [PHONE BEEPS]
- <i>Petey, baby, hi! Remember me?</i>

38:48.034 --> 38:50.489
<i>I bet you do! [LAUGHING]</i>

38:50.490 --> 38:53.539
<i>And of course you remember your mother.</i>

38:53.540 --> 38:55.124
Mom! Mom!

38:55.125 --> 38:56.876
[MOCKING] Mom, Mom?

38:56.877 --> 38:59.209
[LAUGHS] Auntie Em, Auntie Em?

38:59.210 --> 39:00.421
Time's up, fuckhead.

39:00.422 --> 39:01.879
Shoot me in the fucking leg?

39:01.880 --> 39:04.619
<i>Ooh, I ought to slit her
throat just for that.</i>

39:04.620 --> 39:06.939
<i>[EMPHATICALLY] You will be</i>

39:06.940 --> 39:10.180
delivering us the books tomorrow...

39:10.190 --> 39:12.599
<i>or she dies.</i>

39:12.600 --> 39:15.639
<i>You want a second opinion?
Call your old man.</i>

39:15.640 --> 39:18.273
<i>- We might kill him too.</i>
- You fuck!

39:19.400 --> 39:22.479
[SIGHS] Watch your
fucking mouth, you dink.

39:22.480 --> 39:25.110
[GRUNTING]

39:28.500 --> 39:31.036
- [MUFFLED SCREAM]
- Don't you fucking touch her!

39:31.037 --> 39:34.379
Sticks and stones may break my bones,

39:34.380 --> 39:38.199
but words will get the shit
slapped out of your mother.

39:38.200 --> 39:41.899
<i>I will be calling you again at 6:00 a.m.</i>

39:41.900 --> 39:44.674
<i>We will be making a plan
for the book delivery,</i>

39:44.675 --> 39:48.339
<i>a plan that you will execute faithfully,</i>

39:48.340 --> 39:52.579
<i>or it's mommy deadest.</i>

39:52.580 --> 39:55.849
<i>[SMOOCHES] You little fuck.</i>

39:55.850 --> 40:00.980
[PANTING]

40:02.800 --> 40:05.362
[TIRES SQUEAL]

40:13.640 --> 40:15.779
[DOOR OPENS]

40:15.780 --> 40:17.939
[GRUNTS] Hey, buddy.

40:17.940 --> 40:20.859
Marjorie?

40:20.860 --> 40:22.999
Hey, Boogers.

40:23.000 --> 40:24.579
[BOOGERS WHINING]

40:24.580 --> 40:27.160
Here.

40:28.190 --> 40:30.387
[LEASH CLICKS, THUDS]

40:32.930 --> 40:35.929
