40:35.930 --> 40:37.519
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:37.520 --> 40:39.719
Marjorie?

40:39.720 --> 40:46.169
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:46.170 --> 40:47.679
[GRUNTS]

40:47.680 --> 40:54.259
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:54.260 --> 40:56.960
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

41:00.760 --> 41:03.499
Oh, Jesus.

41:03.500 --> 41:06.539
- [WATER RUNNING]
- [KNOCKING ON DOOR]

41:06.540 --> 41:09.600
- [WATER STOPS]
- [DISHES CLATTER]

41:16.725 --> 41:18.509
Got a second?

41:18.510 --> 41:21.813
I'm just finishing up some dishes.

41:23.740 --> 41:25.439
Where's Lou?

41:25.440 --> 41:27.819
[SIGHS] She's taking a bath.

41:27.820 --> 41:28.959
I gave her some bubbles.

41:28.960 --> 41:30.239
Olivia said that there's nothing

41:30.240 --> 41:32.759
a good bubble bath can't cure, so...

41:32.760 --> 41:35.860
Of course, she was wrong. [LAUGHS]

41:36.950 --> 41:40.659
Do you want to tell me what
that was about before?

41:40.660 --> 41:43.799
No, I told you, I do
not want to tell you.

41:43.800 --> 41:47.019
Tell me anyway.

41:47.020 --> 41:50.299
My personal life is my
personal life, okay?

41:50.300 --> 41:51.889
That's bullshit.

41:51.890 --> 41:53.970
We're all in each other's business here.

41:56.160 --> 41:58.340
You've certainly had your claws in mine.

42:03.680 --> 42:05.065
Holly.

42:15.580 --> 42:17.699
My life...

42:17.700 --> 42:20.899
